Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.73,Default,Sign,20,20,10,,{\bord1.5\an7\fs35}Dear Mr. Junichi Katsuragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.73,Default,Sign,20,20,10,,{\bord1.5\an7\fs35}I understand how you probably feel right now. Even if you're right about the way things are, we should still stand up for ourselves. I've decided to form a publishing company, joining forces with a few of our comrades. I would like you to see it as a new weapon in this old and tired battle. I hope you will join me in this endeavor. I want to talk to you about it, face to face.
