Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{part a}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.00,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,A Christmas party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.54,Default,Girl A,0,0,0,,And we're all invited?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.63,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Of course. It's next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:50.34,Default,Girls A-B-C-D,0,0,0,,We'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.55,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,If it's an Olympus party, does that mean you'll play for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.63,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Well, if you have a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.89,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Hey, Ritsu, are you going to the Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.89,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Nishimi invited you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.60,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm not really with their group, so I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:14.03,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't make it. There's a Christmas party at the church that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.24,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Then Kawabuchi can't make it either?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:17.57,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.37,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,We should've checked first...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:25.24,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Maruo. If it's okay with you, I think I would like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.70,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:29.00,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Of course! You're always welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.09,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd say yes, Nishimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.96,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}It'll be better to put some distance between us like this, little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:34.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:40.76,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.18,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You're late, Richie-baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.68,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,H-Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.52,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,All right! Next up is the Spiders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.81,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,What about the Beatles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.19,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Let's do some "Bang Bang Bang!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.03,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Nishimi, want some cider?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.41,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.12,Songs,Seiji,0,0,0,,Feigning innocence, bang bang bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.63,Songs,Seiji,0,0,0,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.22,Songs,Seiji,0,0,0,,He's somebody I just can't beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.39,Songs,Seiji,0,0,0,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.97,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Come on, Nishimi, let's sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.31,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't really know pop songs like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:37.86,Songs,Seiji,0,0,0,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.90,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what he's doing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:44.32,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe he's talking to her at church?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:12.02,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I go to a party alone and all I do is think about those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.69,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.77,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.15,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.44,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What're you doing here? Shouldn't you be at church?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.15,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.49,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,The church's Christmas party is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:29.95,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He isn't here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.71,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Should he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.34,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um... He went home with the little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.26,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.63,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.30,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.05,Default,Sailor,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.14,Default,Sailor,0,0,0,,Gotcha babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.83,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, his birthday's coming up, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.99,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I hope you finish in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.62,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.42,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Why do you say things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.00,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.25,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.34,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Forget it! You're such an idiot, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.85,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did I do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.43,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.27,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Women are just impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.23,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I lose my temper like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:48.32,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the one who rejected him in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:54.25,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I finished this, there's no way I'd be able to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.86,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.70,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're in the clear for now Yurika,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.95,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,but let me tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:31.99,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.49,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,You're going to tell me not to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.50,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,You don't have to keep repeating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.66,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Chet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.29,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.33,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Chet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:53.97,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:55.72,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.48,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,How do you mean? I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.44,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,W-What's with the formality?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.61,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.32,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.75,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I never realized how you felt 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:22.75,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I've said some pretty dumb things and probably hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:27.46,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But... Well, how can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.84,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,But about your feelings, I, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:43.73,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,C'mon, Sentaro, why are you suddenly on your best behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:47.82,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Stop it already. This isn't a mafia movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.11,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Did I get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:54.74,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.41,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:03.08,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,O-Oh, a misunderstanding. Sorry for talkin' all weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:07.75,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,R-Right! We're like family. You made me nervous for a second there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.13,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Wh-What a relief, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:20.35,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,We're like family, so I couldn't stand the thought of hurtin' you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:29.32,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear it now, and not back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.07,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.57,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna tell a blockhead like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.67,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.42,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm going back to Tokyo soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.01,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I probably won't
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.10,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.35,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of the guys from college
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:10.07,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}is starting up his own publishing company and he wants me to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.53,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}I plan on leaving right after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.49,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's taken me a long time to get to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:20.03,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I owe it to you for making me think I should give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.79,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.42,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I don't want to hear you say that, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.67,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't leave me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.46,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could never say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:36.55,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not when he's trying so hard to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.56,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.27,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.35,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.48,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.86,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I threw something away that was very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.19,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, is that girl homeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.53,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Say, Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.62,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Don't mind me. Please, go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:03.95,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,A classy girl like you shouldn't be seen doing something like this, Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:06.96,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.09,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.09,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,P-Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.43,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,It's something important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.18,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yurika...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:24.64,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,So, what am I looking for, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.44,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.69,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.48,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:36.24,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But I'll have to start all over with clean yarn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.74,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Was this going to be a present for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.57,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.24,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Why would you throw away something so important?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.50,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I was confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:58.38,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I realized that it was stupid to knit a gift that I'd never be able to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.51,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't you be able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:04.56,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,B-Because so much has happened between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:07.31,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And I hurt him once already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.27,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}You rejected him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.60,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,And I couldn't just tell him that I like him now, after all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.81,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,so I decided to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.86,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But then I thought that I was making a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:22.57,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,See, there was another time before that when I said nothing and just gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.37,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:29.83,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,No. I'd given up on that a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.00,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It occurred to me that this person has been there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.67,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,to support me all this time, whenever I felt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:43.43,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,When I had no confidence at all, he did his best to encourage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.89,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This time, I want to be the one to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:52.23,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I finally decided to stop being so quiet about my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.74,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for rambling like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.70,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,No, I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.70,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,I think you've opened my eyes a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.08,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.41,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,By the way, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.04,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Who's your prince, Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.92,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.96,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Should I try guessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.42,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,W-W-What are you saying?! Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.26,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{part b}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.85,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm set to leave this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.61,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Working in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.32,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah. A lot happened at college and I ended up dropping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:48.95,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But you'll come back once in a while, won't you? Like you've been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.58,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,No. I'm never coming back to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.92,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Kaoru, our sessions were fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.21,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I'll miss seeing you and Sen-boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:02.30,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,so you two better keep playing jazz together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.93,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Brother Jun! Did you tell him you were going back to Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.60,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.11,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What's up, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.53,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's about Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:24.36,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's about to go back to Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.36,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I heard from Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.41,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, ain't got nothin' to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:31.99,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.12,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're gonna let that be the last you see of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.37,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,There's nothin' left to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:42.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You looked up to him as a big brother since you were a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:46.59,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You may never get the chance to see him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.09,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,There'd be no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.47,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Once he's gone, it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.60,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Enough about Brother Jun already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.73,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Let's get started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.82,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,If you don't feel like practicin', I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:18.08,Default,Old Woman,0,0,0,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.71,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I guess some college students from Tokyo have come to demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:25.17,Default,Man,0,0,0,,against letting the nuclear aircraft carrier into port.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.59,Default,Old Woman,0,0,0,,That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:32.47,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}In their eyes, I'm a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.18,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}They may never forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.48,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:45.03,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I can do is search for my own path from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.86,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}using a different set of tools...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.87,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.00,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Here, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.88,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I made it myself, so it might be a little salty... {heh}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.55,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,But if you ain't eatin' it, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.01,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is this really the time to be eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.84,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did you forget what I said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:15.97,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.43,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb! Are you gonna be this stubborn 'til it's too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.73,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Brother Jun is leaving town today or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.19,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,It's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.49,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm taking the night train, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.61,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Sen-boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:35.33,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,this was rather old-fashioned of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.99,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8}Letter of Challenge{shorten this perhaps to "A Challenge" if you want to fit it on the paper}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.37,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I thought it was some kinda joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.16,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,No jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.54,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I wanted to try havin' a real showdown with you, Brother Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.05,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait... You're not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.30,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Am I on time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.84,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I want in on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.41,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is no duet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:03.21,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're seriously duking it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:30.61,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Sorry for causing you so much trouble, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.31,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Tell me about it! And when you reach Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.32,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,first thing you better do is get a haircut!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.53,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.45,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.50,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.15,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'll remember today's session
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.67,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.63,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.30,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Me too, Sen-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.19,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.70,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I told you not to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:19.07,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I have four questions I want you to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:22.58,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,If you try to dodge them, I'll get on this train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.41,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,So be honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.92,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,First of all, why did you tell me not to see you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:35.42,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I hate sad goodbye scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:40.26,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Second question, why didn't you think to take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:44.60,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,The work I'm gonna be doing is kind of a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.31,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Even if I took you with me, there's no guarantee of making a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.48,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Besides, you're still in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.90,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Question number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.40,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do anything more than kiss me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:19:01.20,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Did you avoid touching me because you had already planned to just take off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:05.74,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.75,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.67,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I knew how much you cared about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.29,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.50,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,my last question...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.84,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Won't you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:25.56,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I want you to take good care of your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.98,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I figured you would say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.53,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Now it feels like I've been set free, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.03,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.54,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Thank you, Junichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.70,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.79,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yurika, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.54,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Come out, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.17,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,How dare you embarrass us by walking out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.09,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,in the middle of an arranged marriage meeting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.55,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Calm down, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:04.05,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,We're going back there together, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.06,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yurika, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:19.32,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.88,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I dragged you on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.55,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.22,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,What else is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.60,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,The train's already left the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.77,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:56.48,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Well, when we get there, we'll go to my room first
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.90,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,and maybe I'll have you cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's freezing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.66,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.50,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Think I'll light the heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:21.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{ED}{First frame after To Be Continued}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:28.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I waited for you on that road downhill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:41.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}Our promise to meet after school always held a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:51.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I was weak and distorted, and seemed to easily crack under pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:22:03.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}You were the one who gave me wings then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:12.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I wish I could say I love you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:23.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}while you're looking for a faint light in the sky at dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:35.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}The letter I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:43.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}will never reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}and nothing will ever change
